videos.description: Malik Dunner runs it in from eight yards out to score the first touchdown of the game for Ball State.
videos.headline: Dunner'sTD gives Ball State lead

videos.description: Riley Neal's touchdown pass to Danny Pinter extends the Cardinals' lead.
videos.headline: Neal hits Pinter for 15-yard TD

videos.description: A.J. Erdley scores UAB's first touchdown of the game with a 41-yard run.
videos.headline: Erdely runs for 41-yard TD

videos.description: Garrison Mitchell breaks up Riley Neal's pass to force a turnover on downs for UAB.
videos.headline: UAB make 4th down stop

videos.description: A.J. Erdely runs 18 yards for a Blazers go-ahead touchdown in the second quarter.
videos.headline: Erdely's 2nd TD run puts UAB up

videos.description: Caleb Huntley runs for 52 yards to put Ball State back on top in the second quarter.
videos.headline: Ball State retakes lead with Huntley TD run

videos.description: Ball State's ball boy makes a great catch on a pass thrown away by UAB's QB
videos.headline: Ball boy makes smooth one-handed catch

videos.headline: Gilbert extends Cardinal's lead

videos.description: A.J. Erdely's eight-yard run gives him his third touchdown of the game.
videos.headline: Erdely  runs for his 3rd TD of the game

videos.description: James Gilbert pounds one in the end zone for another Ball State touchdown.
videos.headline: Gilbert punches in 1-yard TD

videos.description: Justin Hall catches Riley Neal's second touchdown pass of the afternoon.
videos.headline: Hall tip toes down sideline for Ball State touchdown

videos.headline: Copeland runs for 7-yard TD
